acceptance_criteria: "copyExtensionDirectoryWithoutSelfNesting canonicalizes temporaryDirectory (realpath with root-to-leaf fallback, same helper as destination) before the staging-base containment check; extension-copy-safety.spec.ts 'moves staging outside a source that contains the configured temp directory' passes on macOS/Node24 and windows/Node24 nightly legs; no spec-side-only masking"
